descriptionHtml:
Hrothgar only has 4 people in it and is very small. Most low end rigs should be able to use this. A toaster might have his problems though. Dunno about calculators or printers.

Update1: VoltarDaedra spent endless hours making Elfx parallax meshes, appreciate his work. It's a very big improvement for HighHrothgar.
They are complete now, just overwrite all meshes with the new ones. Don't worry about them being elfx, they are compatible to everything and don't overwrite anything else, basically just some lightsources have been improved and added.



[youtube]TgtlUjuVuLo?vq=hd1080&autoplay=0[/youtube]
